%% Diagram: Failure Cascade Sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Audit as Config\naudit tool
    participant BB as Backbone\nrouters
    participant Edge as Edge facility\n(authoritative DNS)
    participant Peer as IXP / upstream\npeers
    participant Resolver as Recursive\nresolvers
    participant User as Browser /\napp

    Audit->>BB: Apply maintenance command\n(audit bug fails to block)
    BB-->>BB: All inter-DC links go down
    Edge->>BB: Health probe (data center reachable?)
    BB--xEdge: TIMEOUT
    Note over Edge: Safety policy:\nno reach => no advertise
    Edge->>Peer: BGP UPDATE\n(withdraw DNS prefixes)
    Peer-->>Peer: Withdrawal propagates\n15:42 -> 15:53:47 UTC
    Resolver->>Edge: Query a.ns.facebook.com\n(after TTL expiry)
    Resolver--xEdge: No route to\n129.134.30.0/24
    Resolver-->>User: SERVFAIL
    User->>Resolver: Aggressive retries\n(~30x normal volume)
